00:36:31.668 --> 00:36:35.168
Even though you don't have much class I on the cell surface, the

616
00:36:35.248 --> 00:36:38.288
mRNA vaccine still gives a big CD8

617
00:36:39.148 --> 00:36:41.348
tetramer response. So that's pretty weird.

618
00:36:42.368 --> 00:36:44.408
So where is the peptide MHC coming from?

619
00:36:45.188 --> 00:36:49.068
I didn't believe this at first, but Suwen proved it to me by making a

