00:37:07.900 --> 00:37:10.740
genetically deficient in class I MHC.

626
00:37:11.560 --> 00:37:11.760
And

627
00:37:14.280 --> 00:37:17.780
this here is to show you that that bone marrow chimer worked

628
00:37:17.790 --> 00:37:21.560
perfectly. So all of the dendritic cells that are coming in these

629
00:37:21.620 --> 00:37:24.340
mice are coming from the bone marrow.

630
00:37:25.800 --> 00:37:26.660
But here's the point.

631
00:37:28.740 --> 00:37:30.440
Here we're doing a specific control.

632
00:37:30.580 --> 00:37:31.620
We're using a dead

633
00:37:32.480 --> 00:37:34.540
mRNA vaccine as a control,

634
00:37:35.680 --> 00:37:37.949
because this shouldn't give a response,

635
00:37:38.780 --> 00:37:40.400
because it's not inducing antigen.

636
00:37:40.420 --> 00:37:43.460
And in the wild type, that's true, it doesn't give an antigen.

