00:38:00.760 --> 00:38:04.630
tetramer. Now, I don't know if one minus two

643
00:38:04.740 --> 00:38:06.580
thirds is one third, but

644
00:38:07.660 --> 00:38:10.940
this size of the response is

645
00:38:11.340 --> 00:38:12.020
substantial.

646
00:38:13.100 --> 00:38:15.240
So we would just guess or

647
00:38:16.360 --> 00:38:20.020
speculate that a substantial amount of the

648
00:38:21.280 --> 00:38:25.160
response in this model system of mRNA vaccine is actually

649
00:38:25.200 --> 00:38:27.110
coming from a cross-dressed

650
00:38:27.920 --> 00:38:31.720
MHC peptide complex from some other cell onto the dendritic

651
00:38:31.740 --> 00:38:31.940
cell.

652
00:38:33.700 --> 00:38:36.250
Okay, so I've told you that DC1s and DC2s

653
00:38:37.360 --> 00:38:37.540
can

654
00:38:40.020 --> 00:38:43.680
mediate the CD8 response. Why should we care who

