00:39:45.990 --> 00:39:49.980
that number one, DC2s start to present

673
00:39:49.990 --> 00:39:52.690
the class II peptide to CD4 T cells.

674
00:39:53.520 --> 00:39:56.770
And that this is a bad thing because in that setting

675
00:39:56.860 --> 00:39:59.240
here or here,

676
00:40:01.380 --> 00:40:03.500
the mice can't reject the tumor anymore.

677
00:40:04.020 --> 00:40:07.300
And he proved that this was due to presentation by the

678
00:40:07.320 --> 00:40:11.160
DC2 because he used our mouse that doesn't

679
00:40:11.220 --> 00:40:15.020
have any DC2s. That's this Delta 123 in the black arrows

680
00:40:15.060 --> 00:40:18.740
here. And those mice, even at the high dose treatment,

681
00:40:19.040 --> 00:40:20.920
are able to prime. So DC2s

682
00:40:22.340 --> 00:40:23.920
are not good

683
00:40:25.140 --> 00:40:25.520
in this

684
00:40:26.660 --> 00:40:28.300
model system. I'm going to skip that.

685
00:40:28.620 --> 00:40:30.060
That's another Gemini

