00:40:31.160 --> 00:40:32.860
model slide, which didn't work out.

687
00:40:34.640 --> 00:40:36.210
So the point is that

688
00:40:37.920 --> 00:40:39.320
there are certain things to consider.

689
00:40:40.340 --> 00:40:42.089
Now in our model system,

