00:40:59.100 --> 00:41:01.500
a tumor. That's what's shown here and here.

696
00:41:02.020 --> 00:41:05.440
So it's not like a completely ineffective CD8 T cell response.

697
00:41:05.520 --> 00:41:07.530
But we wanted to know, are there any

