00:42:22.400 --> 00:42:24.400
effectors are in these shades of blue.

721
00:42:25.640 --> 00:42:25.800
So,

722
00:42:28.820 --> 00:42:29.260
first of all,

723
00:42:30.280 --> 00:42:33.540
we carried out just a global comparison

724
00:42:33.600 --> 00:42:37.580
between the different fractions of these populations, between

