00:43:10.652 --> 00:43:14.552
primed by the ones you should be primed by, by the DC1, you get a better

736
00:43:14.872 --> 00:43:15.792
proliferative

737
00:43:16.692 --> 00:43:19.072
capacity of your early effectors.

738
00:43:19.472 --> 00:43:20.432
You get a greater

739
00:43:21.772 --> 00:43:25.352
population of your stem-likes and fewer effector cells.

740
00:43:25.412 --> 00:43:28.912
So I'm going to end there. Here are my take-home

741
00:43:28.952 --> 00:43:32.372
messages. mRNA vaccines engage both DC1s and

