00:43:51.352 --> 00:43:54.832
primed by DC2s might have weaker memory

748
00:43:54.952 --> 00:43:56.092
responses, for example.

749
00:43:57.732 --> 00:43:59.352
And there's still a lot of work to do.

750
00:43:59.472 --> 00:44:02.932
So I've just run out of time, and I'm going to stop there.

